title: Progressive® Wedge and Pop
description:
Perfect for fresh apple and apple pie lovers. Simple and safe tool quickly slices an apple into eight wedges and cores it too. Push down on apple to cut and swing the cover forward and pop the wedges out. Works great for apples and pears. Handles are comfortable to hold.

The featured product can be purchased at: http://www.surlatable.com/product/PRO-195070/Progressive-Wedge-and-Pop
